description: This Chainlink VRF common Gaston purrs with a rating of 24, and a multiplier of 2x. It has a total score of 48, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are Box for North, 8 for East, 3 for South, and Leverage for West. Gaston has the personality suit of whale. A rendering of the card can be found at https://cards.ethercats.eth.link/60242-48360-3.html. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random NFTs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Gaston [48 Votes, Common]
